OL,4,G1155FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GTony and Paula host the week's
OL,6,     Gthird visit at Hotel Ellenby in
OL,7,     GScarborough, where they reckon
OL,8,     Gstunning sea views and local
OL,9,     Ghistory will be a winning
OL,10,     Gcombination. The breakfast, not
OL,11,     Gso much.
OL,12,G1230FFour in a Bed
OL,13,     GThe week's final visit is to The
OL,14,     GCrown Inn in Derbyshire, where a
OL,15,     Gtrip to an old mill proves to be
OL,16,     Ginexplicably popular. More so
OL,17,     Gthan Dean's supposedly legendary
OL,18,     Gbreakfast, anyway...
